{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255990/extras/MinerCoverShoot-1.png?t=1735917210\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game has a brand new mode of playing. That's constructed with various interesting tools, land blocks and barriers,  and mechanics. Player need to collect tools to break Barriers, manipulate mechanics or make aerial actions to get to hard-to-reach place, or find path in complex scenes, before they get treasure chests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different parts of the scene and factors are restrictive for each other, and maybe they are needed by each other. It slightly tests the player's memory and logic thought. To make progress, player must carefully explore the scene. And that makes the scene more replayable. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are diverse level style in this game. Some are pile of boxes, some like a maze, some are more about action and mechanics, even racing level. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Another interesting part of this game is action elements. This is a precise platformer, so you need to calculate the distance and plan your move before you make a jump, and it's associated with puzzle. Some special tools just like speed shoes\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255990/extras/speedShoes1.png?t=1735917210\" /> or rocket pack\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255990/extras/rocketBag_1.png?t=1735917210\" /> may help you complete that stunt movements in the air.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is an interesting pixel mode to change all the picture to pixel style. So you can experience the feeling of 1990s' classic games, like Mario Bros. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are 28 well-designed levels with increasing difficulty, the final few levels are challenging. All the going through lasts for more than 16 hours. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game has a relaxing atmosphere, and easy to learn how to play. Player can enjoy the fun of finding treasures and smashing something to decrease pressure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255990/extras/startSceneChest-2.png?t=1735917210\" />\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255990/extras/bouncePF.png?t=1735917210\" />\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255990/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735917210","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255990/page.bg.jpg?t=1735917210","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255990/540b39f3f49d88beb5e24e340fb213e77b78d328/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735917210","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255990/540b39f3f49d88beb5e24e340fb213e77b78d328/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735917210","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3357140,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255990/extras/